  "novel_contributions": [
    "We present an improved version of MViT that incorporates decomposed relative positional embeddings and residual pooling connections.",
    "We study MViT as a unified architecture for image and video classification, as well as object detection.",
    "We develop a simple-yet-effective Hybrid window attention scheme that can complement pooling attention for better accuracy/compute tradeoff.",
    "We instantiate the architecture in five sizes and report a practical training recipe for large multiscale transformers."
  ],
  "key_claims": [
    {
      "claim": "MViTv2 is a unified architecture for image and video classification, as well as object detection, and the improved pooling attention uses decomposed relative positional embeddings and residual pooling connections.",
      "evidence_section": "Abstract",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "Without bells-and-whistles, MViTv2 has state-of-the-art performance in 3 domains: 88.8% accuracy on ImageNet classification, 58.7 APbox on COCO object detection, and 86.1% on Kinetics-400 video classification.",
      "evidence_section": "Abstract",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "MViTv2 outperforms prior work on ImageNet-1K, COCO detection, and Kinetics video recognition, and pooling attention outperforms window attention in accuracy/compute.",
      "evidence_section": "Abstract",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "The paper instantiates MViTv2 in five sizes and reports that the improved architecture scales from Tiny to Huge variants.",
      "evidence_section": "4.4. MVIT Architecture Variants",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "On ImageNet-1K, MViTv2-L † 384² reaches 86.3 with full-sized crop testing and is described as the highest accuracy on IN-1K to date without external data or distillation models.",
      "evidence_section": "5.1. Image Classification on ImageNet-1K",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "On COCO, MViTv2-L††* achieves 58.7 APbox with Cascade Mask R-CNN, SoftNMS, and multi-scale testing.",
      "evidence_section": "5.2. Object Detection on COCO",
      "page": null
    },
    {
      "claim": "On Kinetics-400, MViTv2-L reaches 86.1% top-1 accuracy, and on Kinetics-600 and Kinetics-700 the larger models reach 87.9% and 79.4% top-1 respectively.",
      "evidence_section": "6. Experiments: Video Recognition",
      "page": null
    }
  ]
